title: AKAI mpc 5000 Harddisk Backup Loopmasters.zip
description:
akai mpc 5000 loopmasters backup
Backup of the harddrive contents of the MPC 5000 by AKAI.
No CD-ROM is added to restore this. Owners of the MPC 5000 can legally download this file to bring the old loops, samples and sounds back to the internal harddrive. Just download this, unzip, and move the folder 'Loopmasters' to the root of the USB attached MPC 5000 drive.
